# ── Agent scratch / working state — NEVER commit ─────────────────────────────
# A bot once dumped ~28,000 of these into a PR (#259): OpenClaw working dirs, its
# memory notes, scraped feeds, RDF sample exports, ad-hoc patch/debug scripts.
# These are agent scratch, not sources. `.openclaw/` (no leading slash) matches
# at any depth; the anchored dirs only ignore the repo-root scratch versions.
.openclaw/
/memory/
/sample/
/mcp/
/feeds/
*_master.py
add-z

